Get a new one instead of an old cracked one. Someone was kind and sent me
two used ones but one was too thin and the other too dried out. It's a
pretty tight fit if you can find a juicy one.

I measured the good one I found (48mm ID, 52.75mm OD, 2.65mm thick) if
anyone cares.

